    "At the outbreak to World War II, Klein served in the Romanian military, initially a neutral country.": [],
    "When Romania joined the Axis, he was identified as a Jew by the Reich-allied government and worked as forced labor.": [],
    "After a coup in 1944 leading to the country's joining the Allies, Klein was liberated.": [],
    "He subsequently volunteered in the defense of Hungary and Czechoslovakia until the end of the war.": [],
